{% set itemContent %}
  {% include "@bolt-components-headline/headline.twig" with {
    text: "Special Hero!!!",
    size: "xxxlarge",
  } only %}
  <p>Create a special hero with bleeding image by setting <code>valign-self</code> on layout items. It includes offset options to make a layout item positioned to an edge.</p>
